				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$c_e \in {\mathbb {R}}$$\end{document}ce∈R whose sign will determine the preferred direction of transportation. Such a drift term modifies the boundary conditions at each vertex according to\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
